From bb5f26f80b96bb232ddca41483873d35841d4d18 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Beerio Build <assistant@local>
Date: Sun, 28 Jun 2026 23:25:46 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Add format settings, QR spectator view, match history;
 fix touch/portrait

- Best-of-N series scoring (Single / Best of 3 / Best of 5) for WB+LB matches
- 4-Kart heat format option alongside 1v1 Duel
- localStorage persistence (survives refresh; skipped in spectator mode)
- Spectator view: state encoded in URL hash, shareable via QR code modal
- Collapsible match history at page bottom
- touch-action:manipulation on interactive elements; kiosk viewport
- rotate-to-landscape blocker for portrait tablets
- Grand Final relabeled (First to 2 / WB starts 1-0) instead of misleading 'Best of 3'
- New deps: qrcode.react, lz-string
