Backend (artifacts/api-server):
- sessions store with Postgres/Drizzle, in-memory fallback when no DATABASE_URL
- REST routes: POST /api/sessions (create room), PUT/:code (host push), GET/:code (poll)
- serve the built SPA + /api on one origin for autoscale-friendly single-port deploy

DB (lib/db): sessions table (code pk, state jsonb, timestamps)

Frontend (artifacts/beerio-kart):
- 📺 share creates a live room; QR points to /?s=CODE
- host PUTs state on every change (debounced); spectators poll every 3s, read-only
- live status indicators; one-time snapshot link kept as offline fallback
- vite dev proxy /api -> :5000

Root: build:web/build:api/build:all/start/prod/dev scripts; replit.md run+arch notes

